Here is simple clone of digg.com or other news-like site.
So, what's it:
1.User cat register with email/password. Also he can input their full name, but it's not necessarily.
2. Registered user can change him email, password and fullname.
3. Registered user can add news.
4. All users can vote for news up or down.
5. In main page you can see news with only positive rate. For see all news you must link to all_news.
6. All users can comment all news.
